TIGO Tanzania has unveiled a 90 day campaign dubbed ‘Cha Asubuhi’ where every active customer will receive bonus of free minutes and data package upon purchase of a daily, weekly or monthly package. Tigo Tanzania, Acting Chief Commercial Officer said, David Umoh, “We are always looking out for innovative ways to reward our active customers and the campaign offers us a good opportunity to connect with new and existing subscribers.” This campaign gives early risers and those who prefer to plan their day-to-day undertakings in the morning a boost to jump-start their day. The campaign will run for 90 days and is open to all new and existing Tigo customers.